Problem Statement For Hackathon : FS-02 Healthcare Appointment Overbooking Stabilizer
Problem Hospitals overbook appointments to maximize efficiency, leading to conflicts, 
long wait times, and patient dissatisfaction. Design a system that intelligently 
manages overbooked slots and dynamically reschedules patients while 
maintaining fairness and minimizing disruption.
Key Features • Appointment booking system with capacity-aware slot management and 
handling a concurrent cancellation storm
* Doctor availability tracking with real-time updates & Doctor fatigue 
optimization 
* Queue visualization with wait-time prediction
* Overbooking conflict resolver balancing priority vs. fairness
* Dynamic rescheduling engine that minimizes patient disruption
